Conclusion

Learn what could be done to master the system design interview further.

Great! You have almost completed the course. You have learnt what an SDI is with the help of the DoorDash use case.

Let’s conclude with what we can do further to for learn more about system design interviews.

System design interviews are very challenging and thought-provoking and really give the interviewer a sneak peek into the technical acumen of the interviewee. The best way to prepare for this kind of interview is to start enjoying designing big popular day-to-day applications and thinking about millions of users, huge datasets, points of failure, transactions, and so forth. Hopefully, this course has given you some ideas about how you can go about tackling such interviews. You can’t master system design until you practice a lot. If you want to get more practice of SDI, Educative.io has several system design courses that you can explore.
